race.comment: KALANI SKY (5) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (29.79) at this track in Maiden over 515m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Well placed and can measure up. BURST ON TURBO (1) is better than last start when seventh (30.30) from Box 3 at this track over 515m. Has ability and can measure up. CESSNOCK CURTAIN (8) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the minors latest when second (29.83) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Winning chance. BLAZING PRINCE (3) failed despite market confidence last time but can do better.
